01:26:42.290 --> 01:26:44.160
Feu à volonté !

01:26:51.090 --> 01:26:52.590
Technique à deux sabres,

01:27:00.510 --> 01:27:01.890
Falcon Waves !

01:27:12.660 --> 01:27:16.370
