FALCON WAVES

01:27:19.160 --> 01:27:21.070
Me voilà bien encerclé.

01:27:21.240 --> 01:27:23.030
Chargez !

01:27:25.330 --> 01:27:27.250
Soul Solid…

01:27:38.010 --> 01:27:39.590
Swallow…

01:27:39.880 --> 01:27:41.340
Bond avant !

